node_modules
*.log

# NOTE: dist/ is intentionally NOT ignored.
# funny installs the pre-built bundle straight from the repo (CI never builds on
# install — same model as VSCode .vsix / Obsidian release artifacts), so the
# committed dist/ is what users get. Run `npm run build` and commit dist/ before
# tagging a release. The CI workflow fails if the committed dist/ is stale.
